text: LaPorte County is a county located in the U.S. state of Indiana. As of 2020, the population was 112,417. The county seat is the city of La Porte, and the largest city is Michigan City. This county is part of the Northwest Indiana and Michiana regions of the Chicago metropolitan area. ==References== Category:Indiana counties Category:1830s establishments in Indiana Category:1832 establishments in the United States
title: LaPorte County, Indiana
